{"tid":881883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊境部署5000士兵 川普警告中美洲難民:美軍正等著你們","createTime":"2018-10-29T19:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T08:22:35.000Z","uid":5195,"like":110,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"c2caf04a899e1fe65e458c3e36a405a0ee67ac6e","tid":881883,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T19:02:06.000Z","msg":"「請掉頭吧」，美國總統川普（特朗普）29日發推文對「大篷車」人群說。為了阻止中美洲大篷車人群試圖非法入境美國，傳美國軍方計劃在美墨邊境部署5,000名士兵。川普告誡中美洲人，如果他們非法越境，其行為是對美國的入侵，美軍會應對危機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國防部長馬蒂斯（Jim Mattis）上週同意國土安全部的請求，加派軍力到美墨邊境。週一（10月29日），一名美國官員告訴《華爾街日報》，國防部將派5,000名現役軍人到美墨邊境，大約是目前在邊境執法的海關官員人數的三分之一。<br />\n<br />\n美軍派5,000人守南界，這個數字遠超過上週初步估計的800到1,000人。軍方在今年稍早已派了2,000名國民警衛隊到美墨邊境。五角大樓發言人表示，有關部署兵力的實際數據，目前都「言之過早」。<br />\n<br />\n總統川普29日上午再次針對大篷車事件發推文說：「許多幫派分子及一些非常壞的傢伙想要混入大篷車車隊，向我們的南部邊境前進。請掉頭吧，除非你們通過法律程序，否則美國不會允許你們進入美國。這是對我們國家的入侵，我們的軍隊正在等著你們！」"},{"pid":"fcf3dc29112f84a5e3ed5478a8ceea8fb151324c","tid":881883,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T22:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e71359894c70ed7143e5163f96dc207b84a1f9","tid":881883,"uid":73092,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T22:17:18.000Z","msg":"侵侵先係正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb85872fbe9a3ef1c5f966c3a4c8d1e73b2f6c5","tid":881883,"uid":20241,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:07:05.000Z","msg":"左膠等緊發大黎搞"},{"pid":"fbaa05491a81f74a64289278167c188de1cd8cd3","tid":881883,"uid":131157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355bc462674c4879ce13c7ddeef5e48a851cf15d","tid":881883,"uid":58552,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:38:30.000Z","msg":"左膠發動 手牽手人肉護送難民"},{"pid":"1297f42e827e3e45b279052a025afa57d38465f5","tid":881883,"uid":11097,"like":82,"dislike":1,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:39:00.000Z","msg":"啱啦！有咩你咪用正常程序入美國囉<br />\n佢講得無錯喎<br />\n我地香港人日日俾共狗攪都冇得話係因為英國棄民/用BNO衝入英國住啦，你班墨佬憑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873e3dfb7a2392fb9f22ee98a081610d24eac7d0","tid":881883,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:39:40.000Z","msg":"左膠協助偷渡"},{"pid":"f42aa3d4bce198462a33f79f29f241e657359b4a","tid":881883,"uid":68598,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:55:44.000Z","msg":"送埋左膠去邊境 睇佢地既大愛係果度發揮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8fff52a7b17b871d6576fc60e337e5ccb63684","tid":881883,"uid":95497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:59:11.000Z","msg":"炮決<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb39e3b1cbe9aab17de79d8b92c1f9a4dafbcd7","tid":881883,"uid":21028,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:03:55.000Z","msg":"啱架啦 非法入境 仲洗撚投資移民"},{"pid":"d680202c19c49d8a6d44afed7290d138c4548e5d","tid":881883,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:06:31.000Z","msg":"如果開槍實被人公審<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541f6f495f38c8cd510cdbe73fc11a9e54c074c8","tid":881883,"uid":53687,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"f42aa3d4bce198462a33f79f29f241e657359b4a","tid":881883,"uid":68598,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:55:44.000Z","msg":"送埋左膠去邊境 睇佢地既大愛係果度發揮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:28:22.000Z","msg":"安排佢哋一換一，睇下班大愛撚仲敢唔敢嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5701477e97b6c8a768babb797f4a63d79c849015","tid":881883,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike"